 main-nav-button w-nav-link\">Order Now</a></nav><div class=\"menu-button w-nav-button\"><div class=\"w-icon-nav-menu\"></div></div></div></div><section class=\"page-header wf-section\"><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f50d51e8e1f51468519a5_hdr-original-n-fries.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f50d51e8e1f51468519a5_hdr-original-n-fries-p-500.jpg 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f50d51e8e1f51468519a5_hdr-original-n-fries-p-800.jpg 800w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f50d51e8e1f51468519a5_hdr-original-n-fries-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f50d51e8e1f51468519a5_hdr-original-n-fries-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f50d51e8e1f51468519a5_hdr-original-n-fries.jpg 1920w\" class=\"page-header-image\"/><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f5db96165eaf4d5fcde5d_hdr-original-n-fries-sm.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f5db96165eaf4d5fcde5d_hdr-original-n-fries-sm-p-500.jpg 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f5db96165eaf4d5fcde5d_hdr-original-n-fries-sm-p-800.jpg 800w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f5db96165eaf4d5fcde5d_hdr-original-n-fries-sm-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f5db96165eaf4d5fcde5d_hdr-original-n-fries-sm-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f5db96165eaf4d5fcde5d_hdr-original-n-fries-sm.jpg 1920w\" class=\"page-header-image-small\"/><div class=\"page-header-container w-container\"><h1 class=\"page-header-text\">Our Menu</h1><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408a99d68e95ec7851c3fde_diamond-divider-7ct.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"divider-diamonds\"/><div class=\"page-header-intro\">Welome to The Budlong. A Nashville Hot Chicken Joint.</div></div></section><section class=\"inset-section wf-section\"><div class=\"inset-section-inner inset-black w-container\"><p class=\"white text-centered\">Hot Chicken is enjoyably spicy, deliciously crispy, fried chicken - first served in the music city. We use locally sourced, hand-battered chicken. Our sides and desserts are made from scratch with love. Choose your level of heat and enjoy the southern comfort &amp; hospitality!</p></div></section><section class=\"default-section wf-section\"><div class=\"default-section-inner w-container\"><div class=\"flex-row\"><div class=\"flex-item-one-half\"><div class=\"flex-item-inner\"><h2 class=\"red\">Sandwiches</h2><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/64089b9ee4cf6a80ecf5eeab_BudlongOriginal_white-bg.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 79vw, 320px\" srcset=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/64089b9ee4cf6a80ecf5eeab_BudlongOriginal_white-bg-p-500.jpg 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/64089b9ee4cf6a80ecf5eeab_BudlongOriginal_white-bg-p-800.jpg 800w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/64089b9ee4cf6a80ecf5eeab_BudlongOriginal_white-bg-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/64089b9ee4cf6a80ecf5eeab_BudlongOriginal_white-bg.jpg 1280w\" alt=\"The Budlong Original Chicken Sandwich\" class=\"menu-image\"/><p>All sandwiches are hand-breaded using our secret Budlong recipe and served on a buttered-and-toasted brioche bun. Choose either the original Chicken Breast or the tastier Chicken Thigh (trust us) for any sandwich.<br/></p><p><strong>THIGH \u2014 $6.99 \u00b7 BREAST \u2014 $9.99</strong></p><h3>The Budlong Original</h3><p>Served with our homemade \u201cComeback Sauce\u201d, farm slaw and our famous Budlong pickles.</p><h3>Southern Style</h3><p>Straight outta the south, served with pimiento cheese spread and our famous Budlong pickles.<br/></p><h3>YO\u2019 MAMMA\u2019S</h3><p>This one\u2019s so good, you\u2019ll have to bring one back home. Served with black-pepper pickle relish mayo, lettuce, tomato, red onion and our famous Budlong pickles.</p><p><strong>Add a slice of American cheese for $0.99</strong></p><h2 class=\"red\">Just the Chicken</h2><p>Save your buns \u2013 just do the chicken. Served with buttered-and-toasted Texas Toast and our famous Budlong pickles.</p><h3>CHICKEN TENDERS (2 PIECES) \u2014 $7.99</h3><p>Make it a meal with homemade fries +$1</p><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408a0a668e95e22481bb727_HalfChixDarkTexasToastPickls_white-bg.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 79vw, 320px\" srcset=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408a0a668e95e22481bb727_HalfChixDarkTexasToastPickls_white-bg-p-500.jpg 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408a0a668e95e22481bb727_HalfChixDarkTexasToastPickls_white-bg-p-800.jpg 800w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408a0a668e95e22481bb727_HalfChixDarkTexasToastPickls_white-bg-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408a0a668e95e22481bb727_HalfChixDarkTexasToastPickls_white-bg.jpg 1280w\" alt=\"Half Chicken Dark\" class=\"menu-image\"/><h3>1/4 CHICKEN DARK \u2014 $9.99</h3><p>Make it a meal with homemade fries +$1</p></div></div><div class=\"flex-item-one-half\"><div class=\"flex-item-inner\"><h2 class=\"red\">Everything Else</h2><h3>POPCORN CHICKEN \u2014 $6.99</h3><p>Seriously, what\u2019s not to love here. Our tasty, breaded Chicken pieces with your choice of dipping sauce.</p><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408b78c7780a7b3670ad5ad_SaladPopcornChix_V2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 79vw, 320px\" srcset=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408b78c7780a7b3670ad5ad_SaladPopcornChix_V2-p-500.jpg 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408b78c7780a7b3670ad5ad_SaladPopcornChix_V2-p-800.jpg 800w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408b78c7780a7b3670ad5ad_SaladPopcornChix_V2-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6408b78c7780a7b3670ad5ad_SaladPopcornChix_V2.jpg 1280w\" alt=\"Popcorn Chicken Salad\" class=\"menu-image\"/><h3>SALAD \u2014 $11.99</h3><p>Spring and green leaf lettuce, tomatoes, carrots, cucumbers, red onion and Popcorn Chicken. <strong>Choose your dressing: </strong><em>Buttermilk Ranch, Comeback Sauce, Raspberry Vinaigrette</em></p><h2 class=\"red\">For the Kids</h2><p>For Kid\u2019s 12 years old or younger<br/>\u200d<strong>Chicken Tender served with fries \u2014 $6.99<br/>Chicken Tender served with Mac &amp; Cheese \u2014 $7.99</strong></p><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f67c46677e0e1602480bd_KidsTenderMacChz.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 79vw, 320px\" srcset=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f67c46677e0e1602480bd_KidsTenderMacChz-p-500.jpg 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f67c46677e0e1602480bd_KidsTenderMacChz-p-800.jpg 800w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f67c46677e0e1602480bd_KidsTenderMacChz-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640f67c46677e0e1602480bd_KidsTenderMacChz.jpg 1280w\" alt=\"Kids&#x27;s Tender with Mac&#x27;n&#x27;Cheese\" class=\"menu-image\"/><h3 class=\"red\">Sides &amp; Extras</h3><p>Chicken Tender \u2014 $3.99<br/>Fries \u2014 $2.99<br/>Mac &amp; Cheese \u2014 $3.99<br/>Farm Slaw \u2014 $3.99<br/>Biscuit with strawberry balsamic jam \u2014 $3.99</p><h3 class=\"red\">Dessert</h3><p>Famous Homemade Banana Puddin\u2019 \u2014 $6.99</p><h3 class=\"red\">Beverages</h3><p>Wet your whistle (just ask us what we have) \u2014 $2.99</p></div></div></div></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"spacer-80px\"></div><div class=\"cta-section-inner text-centered w-container\"><h2>Southern-Fried Catering</h2><a href=\"https://www.ezcater.com/brand/pvt/budlong-hot-chicken\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"primary-button w-button\">view Our Catering Menu</a></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"spacer-40px\"></div></section><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"fixed-contact-button w-inline-block\"><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/640ce9aaba45fe42cc931520_icon-envelope-white.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"Auto\" alt=\"\" class=\"contact-button-icon\"/><div class=\"contact-button-text\">Contact Us</div></a><footer class=\"site-footer wf-section\"><div class=\"site-footer-inner w-container\"><div class=\"site-footer-content\"><div class=\"site-footer-column\"><img src=\"https://assets.website-files.com/63f4fe41281895a58ade6797/6401f898371b17326b858657_thebudlong_icon_white.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" alt=\"\" class=\"footer-logo\"/></div><div class=\"site-footer-column\"><ul role=\"list\" class=\"footer-nav w-list-unstyled\"><li class=\"footer-nav-item\"><a href=\"/locations\" class=\"footer-nav-link\">Locations</a></li><li class=\"footer-nav-item\"><a href=\"/menu\" aria-current=\"page\" class=\"footer-nav-link w--current\">Menu</a></li><li class=\"footer-nav-item\"><a href=\"/our-story\" class=\"footer-nav-link\">Our Story</a></li><li class=\"footer-nav-item\"><a href=\"/news\" class=\"footer-nav-link\">In The News</a></li><li class=\"footer-nav-item\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"footer-nav-link\">Contact Us</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"site-footer-column\"><ul role=\"list\" class=\"footer-social w-list-unstyled\"><li class=\"footer-social-item\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thebudlong/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" clas